Colour collection

Source: R/colours.R
cols.Rd

A collection of colours found in various places

Usage

cols()

Examples

names(cols())
#>  [1] "redfocus"         "greenfocus"       "bluefocus"        "rainbow12equal"

#>      red green blue
pal(cols()$tol8)
